   <body>
      <section>
         <indexterm>controller box</indexterm>
      </section>
      <section>
         <p>
            <fig>
               <image href="../Images/powerblockprinciplediagram_120mm_0000116662.svg"
                      scalefit="yes"
                      translate="yes"
                      xml:lang="en"
                      placement="inline"/>
            </fig>
         </p>
         <p>The controller box controls the entire UPS system and
consists of 2 PCBs:<ul>
               <li>
                  <p>Controller board</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>Adapter board</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
         <p>The controller box has the following functions:<ul>
               <li>
                  <p>controls the power modules</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>communicates with the Smart Slot Module (NMC, Modbus)</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>communicates with the HMI</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>communicates with the interface board</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>communicates with the external connection board via the interface
board</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>communicates with the static bypass switch controller</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
      </section>
